                                                         Bufford's Lith. in Boston, 1890-1895.
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                     </table>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="indicatorvalue"><strong>1 - Administrative history</strong> <div class="description">Information in the field is an administrative history of an organization.
                  <div class="example">
                     <table width="100%">
